Description: Zero-day vulnerability discovery engine with 8 detection modules
 OMEGA-ZERODAY is an advanced zero-day vulnerability discovery tool 
 designed for penetration testers and security researchers.
 .
 Features 8 specialized detection engines:
  * ReconSpider - Endpoint discovery, sensitive files, API paths
  * AuthBreaker - Authentication bypass, JWT analysis, header manipulation
  * RaceHunter - Race condition (TOCTOU) detection via parallel bursts
  * SSRFOracle - Server-Side Request Forgery detection
  * MassAssign - Mass assignment and content-type switching
  * SmuggleHunter - HTTP request smuggling (CL.TE, TE.CL, TE.TE)
  * LogicBreaker - Business logic flaw detection
  * CryptoOracle - Cryptographic weakness and timing side-channel analysis
 .
 Built with a high-performance C engine for speed and a Python Rich 
 TUI for beautiful terminal output. Supports JSON output for automation.
 .
 Includes exploit chain analysis that links related vulnerabilities 
 into attack chains for maximum impact assessment.
